-- To Create a Disk Image --

- Create a disk image
- Format it to EXT2
- Write the boot sector to any directory
- Write the kernel to the root directory, it must be named 'dnos_kernel.elf'
- Locate the first sector of the boot loader file on the virtual disk
- Alter the variable at the end of Stage1.asm
- Reassemble Stage1.asm
- Copy Stage1.bin to the first sector of the virtual hard disk
- DNOS should now run
